name: CMYK Project-C
description:
In the CMYK printing process, individually these four colors work fine on their own but together they can make any full color photo. The music for the 4NFTs here are meant to be played all together but work fine individually. Be your own DJ- The composition will be different every time! 

*Sound design by @fendelmarc & @sistersageherbs - Recorded & Mixed in Seattle, WA 

*Art by @mightymoss

Collectors of this NFT may use the music for your own project. Please copy and paste in your description: Sound design by @fendelmarc - Recorded & Mixed in Seattle, WA 

C Instrumentation: Spitfire Labs synthesizer, flexitone, Reyna Zack-vocals, gong “dark star”, goat nails
